00:38:18.000 --> 00:38:22.000 align:middle line:90%
首次大出血或静脉血栓栓塞的复合终点。

00:38:22.000 --> 00:38:23.000 align:middle line:90%
是的。

00:38:23.000 --> 00:38:27.000 align:middle line:90%
